Package: curvr
Type: Package
Title: Calculate Total Curvature From Landmarked Specimens
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Mannfred Masahiro Asada", "Boehm", email = "mannfred.boehm@ubc.ca", 
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Calculates total curvature from landmarked specimens.
    Total curvature can be calculated from 
    interpolating splines, or from the tangent angle function. 
